'''''Swords of Twilight''''' is a 1989 video game developed by [[Free Fall Associates]] and published by [[Electronic Arts]] for the [[Amiga]].

==Gameplay==
''Swords of Twilight'' is a multi-player role-playing game in which each [[player character]] is capable of performing actions, dialogue and travel simultaneously.<ref name="CGW68"/>

==Reception==
